steps.name: I remove the concession for David Wrenn from Billing account
I add a new concession in billing account for David Wrenn
I config the options in Concession Management page
I click on Yes to add the concession
I verify that the phrase Successfuly Added present and take a full screenshot
I click on the Finish Button
I take a full screenshot and close the browser
